{"tid":1306632,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"八達通將可在 iPhone 和 Apple Watch 上使用","createTime":"2019-07-11T08:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T08:39:17.000Z","uid":218612,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"04016a307c915a20fc17adfc84f3ccddb0350cd4","tid":1306632,"uid":218612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"（香港，2019年7月11日）八達通卡有限公司一向致力提供創新的支付服務，以配合客戶多元化支付需要，公司宣布今年稍後，客戶將可在 iPhone 或 Apple Watch 上透過 Apple Pay ，使用八達通支付公共交通及零售交易。公司會於稍後公布更多詳情。<br />\n<br />\n八達通公司新聞稿<br />\n2019年7月11日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/corporate/media/press-releases/2019/20190711.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.octopus.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fcorporate%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2F2019%2F20190711.html&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8526d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=57a9a0ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/corporate/media/press-releases/2019/20190711.html</a>"},{"pid":"dc6018150a7cff2195258177bb1d8d363a94f5a0","tid":1306632,"uid":22362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:25:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母終於都生性"},{"pid":"396a9acfba3f53691051aa31fa15b95dabc43ff2","tid":1306632,"uid":22362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"apple watch將會大賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace31b3294797221591f1e5dd0ed937ae319ff54","tid":1306632,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"反觀Samsung<br />\n隻錶用到Samsung Pay但係冇八達通"},{"pid":"8f9301ce205ae045c861108126c6a6c3a5310366","tid":1306632,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:31:58.000Z","msg":"八達通應該係見港鐵加QR code入閘先識驚無咗壟斷地位"},{"pid":"6c339e36a0f7a849c0a8c2fa18ffcc1a814cccc1","tid":